## 🧮 Sets Library

**Total:** 226 unique sets  
**Categorized:** Kick (66), Mixed (70), Pull (51), IM (17), Sprint (14), Stroke (9), Race-Prep (3), Drill (1)

**Diversity:** 9.8/10 (excellent variety)

### Sample Signature Sets

**Kick Work:**
```
FINS: 8x50 @ 1:10
  25 - Surface free kick build to full speed (alligator eyes, 3 breath max)
  25 - Underwater pull-down, 3 dolphin kicks, FAST breast + free kick
```

**Station Training:**
```
3 Stations (rotate every 5 minutes):
  Station 1: FAST 25 kick + 25 power tower (pound load)
  Station 2: Stretch cordz full speed swim
  Station 3: Running dive + fast swim choice stroke
```

**Pull Work:**
```
PADS: 6x[75+25] @ 1:30/:45
  75 - 1-2-3 pull-downs by 25, add kick breast
  25 - STRONG build (5-6 strokes)
  Odd: Knuckle pulls | Even: Regular
```

**Race-Prep:**
```
3x500 @ 1:00 STRETCH
2-4x75 Broken @ :10/50 rest
(Pace 400/500 with short rest intervals)
```

